title: Dance Your Way Into 2025! | Lincoln, 02865
text:
Dance Your Way Into 2025!
- 1992 Old Louisquisset Pike., Lincoln, 02865
- Blackstone Valley
- January 23, 2025 - February 27, 2025
Dance your way into 2025! Classes are back in action at our studio and registration is open year round. Come explore different styles of movement in a supportive and welcoming environment, make lasting friendships and experience the difference at FDC. Your first class is always free.
